  "texts": [
    "The other fundamental component of the LangChain Agent is memory.",
    "As a conversational assistant, F-One needs to be able to manage a memory state that allows it to remember information communicated by the user during the conversation.",
    "LangChain allows integrating a memory system into an Agent that uses an LLM.",
    "The type of memory that we implemented in F-One is called ConversationBufferWindowMemory.",
    "With this type of memory, the messages exchanged between the Chatbot and the user are collected and passed as raw input to the LLM in each interaction."
  ],
